they moved, and the

00:15:25.020 --> 00:15:25.960
locomotion of them.

00:15:25.960 --> 00:15:29.540
It was because there's dozens
and hundreds of

00:15:29.540 --> 00:15:30.970
monsters in each shot.

00:15:30.970 --> 00:15:33.140
And they all move differently.

00:15:33.140 --> 00:15:34.580
So you have to--

00:15:34.580 --> 00:15:36.980
