sort of the purple

00:15:47.660 --> 00:15:49.200
thing you saw in that--

00:15:49.200 --> 00:15:50.250
KORI RAE: U-shaped guy.

00:15:50.250 --> 00:15:50.510
DAN SCANLON: Yeah.

00:15:50.510 --> 00:15:51.140
KORI RAE: Yeah.

00:15:51.140 --> 00:15:52.060
DAN SCANLON: And that was great
