00:17:03.750 --> 00:17:05.359
Some of it is.

00:17:05.359 --> 00:17:07.390
And a lot of it just happens
because the artists

00:17:07.390 --> 00:17:08.520
are who they are.

00:17:08.520 --> 00:17:09.560
So it's cool that way.

